{
  "stem": "3757.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And just then I became pregnant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we decided, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We don't want to stay in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have to have an abortion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were about 20 young couples.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All-- all of us had skills-- lawyers. technicians, opticians-- all kinds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So everybody had something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, they would never be a burden on any country.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we decided that, as a group, we want to leave Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we gave everywhere-- I think is no country in the world where we didn't apply to permit to move there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everywhere we were, we were refused, including the United States, Australia, New Zealand, Canada-- whatever I can think of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So-- and in 1939, they took already the young men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They come-- 1939 came the second law against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they took in labor camps then in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And in 1940, also my husband was summoned also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And 1941 again, they were in Nagykata-- is the name of this town where they have to go to the-- they was not the army, because they didn't have that men or uniform-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So-- and this was it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then come 1942.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then my husband and-- and other, I think-- I think about 60,000 labor-- in the labor camp, took to Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I never heard about him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I got one-- one little-- I'll show it to you-- a little piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It-- it came to me as soldier and ask for a small amount of money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And in 19-- what about this year-- it was 19-- 1943, I got the official notice that he's missing in action.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But I know they all died there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was cruel, more cruel than any concentration camp-- what they did with these people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
